<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Recoleta:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #121212; /* Set background color */
            font-family: 'Recoleta', sans-serif; /* Use Recoleta font */
            color: white; /* Set text color for better contrast */
            margin: 0; /* Remove default margin */
            padding: 200px; /* Add padding for content spacing */
            position: relative; /* Set position relative for absolute positioning of the image */
        }

        h2, h3 {
            margin: 10px 0; /* Space out headings */
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6; /* Improve readability of paragraphs */
        }

        .logo {
            position: absolute; /* Position the logo absolutely */
            top: 150px; /* Distance from the top */
            left: 50px; /* Distance from the right */
            width: 200px; /* Set width of the logo (adjust as needed) */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            z-index: 10; /* Ensure it appears above other content */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <img src="~/Content/images/Logo.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
    <main aria-labelledby="title">
        <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title</h2>
        <h3>@ViewBag.Message</h3>

        <p>The EHS Group is a professional real estate brokerage serving buyers and sellers of luxury property in Delhi, Gurugram, Pune, Mumbai and Bangalore. The brokerage is composed of a close group of talented Realtors led by the firm’s President and Founder, Jason Oppenheim. With more than $3.5B+ in total sales and $500 million in active listings, the firm closes hundreds of deals annually and has brokered many of the region’s largest residential sales, including numerous record-breaking transactions. With offices in West Hollywood, Newport, San Diego, and Cabo San Lucas, The Oppenheim Group is the preeminent brokerage in the region, doing tremendous business throughout Metro cities in India.</p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>